data.description: Don't miss this well maintained updated true ranch home on over 1/2 and acre of land. Backyard is level and fenced. Step inside to beautiful hardwood floors. Open floor plan with kitchen overlooking the eat in kitchen and living room. Huge additional bonus space for extra living area, work out area, office or family room. Master bedroom is oversized with master bath and shower. Spacious secondary bedrooms. Home features newer water heater and roof. No HOA. Close to shopping. Do not miss this opportunity!
